metadata.name: Kiki HUMBL
metadata.description:
Tickeri's new home is represented in Kiki's Humbl NFT. The Tickeri familia and Kiki are so excited, happy and humbled for joining the Humbl brand. Quoting Kiki: "the cielo is the limit", and we cannot agree more. 
This is the FIRST HUMBL x Tickeri NFT.  This NFT will include a signed postcard from Brian Foote with an exclusive 2021 Kiki + HUMBL sticker.
